<!-- MainCellStart --><TD VALIGN='TOP'><CENTER><table border=0 cellpadding=5 bgcolor=#DDDDDD width=50% background='/images/table-head-bg.jpg'><tr><td background=''><table border=0 cellpadding=5 bgcolor=#BB0000 width=100%><tr><td width=50% background='/images/table-bg.jpg'><b><font size=+3 color=#FFF000><center>What Is EverMon?<center></font></b></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></center><HR SIZE=1 WIDTH=80%></CENTER><BR><B><U><FONT SIZE=+1>About EverMon</FONT></U></B><BR>

<P>&nbsp&nbsp EverMon is an EverQuest Server Monitoring Utility.  It's
purpose is to let users know when the Patch, Chat, World, and Zone servers
that make up EverQuest are up or down.  It also includes several other
abilities such as :</p>

 <ul>
 <li>Ability to show how many users are currently on the chat server
 <li>Ability to show how many users are on each world server
 <li>Ability to show how many zones are down for each world
 <li>Ability to automatically launch EverQuest when selected servers are up
 <li>Ability to receive real-time news and information updates about server status and down times
 </ul><br>

 <center><image src="evermon1.jpg"></center><br>

You can access the Online <a href=em_help.htm target=main>EverMon Help File</a> for more information.

